name: r-phylogeneticem
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.5.0" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-phylogeneticem
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/PhylogeneticEM_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/PhylogeneticEM/PhylogeneticEM_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: fc8616f958210a1185a3f943cbc34287a4ca966e1876fa0d0803e927b5368db9

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 0
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}              # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}            # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_cxx') }}      # [win]
    - {{ posix }}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}make
    - {{ posix }}sed               # [win]
    - {{ posix }}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-linselect >=1.1.1
    - r-mass >=7.3.45
    - r-matrix >=1.2.3
    - r-rcpp >=1.0.2
    - r-rcpparmadillo
    - r-ape >=5.3
    - r-capushe >=1.1.1
    - r-foreach >=1.4.3
    - r-gglasso >=1.4
    - r-glmnet >=2.0.5
    - r-plyr >=1.8.4
    - r-robustbase >=0.92.6
  run:
    - r-base
    - {{ native }}gcc-libs         # [win]
    - r-linselect >=1.1.1
    - r-mass >=7.3.45
    - r-matrix >=1.2.3
    - r-rcpp >=1.0.2
    - r-rcpparmadillo
    - r-ape >=5.3
    - r-capushe >=1.1.1
    - r-foreach >=1.4.3
    - r-gglasso >=1.4
    - r-glmnet >=2.0.5
    - r-plyr >=1.8.4
    - r-robustbase >=0.92.6

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('PhylogeneticEM')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('PhylogeneticEM')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/pbastide/PhylogeneticEM
  license: GPL-2.0-or-later
  summary: Implementation of the automatic shift detection method for Brownian Motion (BM) or Ornstein–Uhlenbeck (OU) models of trait evolution on phylogenies. Some tools to handle equivalent shifts configurations are also available. See Bastide et al. (2017) <doi:10.1111/rssb.12206> and Bastide et al. (2018) <doi:10.1093/sysbio/syy005>.
  license_family: GPL2
  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2
    - LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
